{"slug":"sirkuler-26-250","reference":"Sirkuler_26_0248","gazette":"13 Nisan 2026 Tarihli ve E-16934678-163.01.01-00121070325 sayılı Uluslararası Anlaşmalar ve Avrupa Birliği Genel Müdürlüğü Yazısı","title":"Basitleştirilmiş Usulde Düzenlenen A.TR Dolaşım Belgeleri","date":"15 Nisan 2026","bodyHtml":"<p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:7.25pt;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:.25pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:35.4pt;line-height:\r\n115%\">Covid-19 salgını süresince İtalya’da onaylanmış ihracatçı statüsüne sahip\r\nfirmalara tanınan, kendi ihracatları dışındaki işlemler için de\r\nbasitleştirilmiş usulde A.TR düzenleme imkânı, Avrupa Komisyonu tarafından 1\r\nMayıs 2024 tarihi itibarıyla kaldırılmıştır. <o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:7.25pt;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:.25pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:35.4pt;line-height:\r\n115%\">Söz konusu geçici uygulama nedeniyle özellikle A.TR belgelerinin 13 no.lu\r\nhanesinin doldurulması konusunda uygulamada tereddütler oluştuğu tespit\r\nedilmiştir. <o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:7.25pt;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:.25pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:35.4pt;line-height:\r\n115%\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:7.25pt;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:.25pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:35.4pt;line-height:\r\n115%\"><b>Mevzuat Çerçevesi</b><o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:7.25pt;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:36.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:\r\n115%;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\r\nSymbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol\">·<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]-->2006/10895 sayılı Karar kapsamında: <o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:7.25pt;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:72.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:\r\n115%;mso-list:l1 level2 lfo1;tab-stops:list 72.0pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\r\n&quot;Courier New&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Courier New&quot;\">o<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]-->A.TR\r\nbelgesinin (13) no.lu “İhracatçının Beyanı” hanesi ihracatçı tarafından\r\nimzalanır. <o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:7.25pt;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:72.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:\r\n115%;mso-list:l1 level2 lfo1;tab-stops:list 72.0pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\r\n&quot;Courier New&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Courier New&quot;\">o<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]-->Belge\r\nüzerinde elektronik sistem dışında herhangi bir ekleme/düzeltme yapılamaz. <o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:7.25pt;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:36.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:\r\n115%;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\r\nSymbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol\">·<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]-->Basitleştirilmiş usulde düzenlenen ve (13) no.lu\r\nhanesi onaylanmış ihracatçı tarafından imzalanan belgeler, gümrük idaresince\r\nvize edilen A.TR ile eşdeğer kabul edilmektedir. <o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:7.25pt;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:.25pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:35.4pt;line-height:\r\n115%\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:7.25pt;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:.25pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:35.4pt;line-height:\r\n115%\"><b>Esas Uygulama Kuralları</b><o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:7.25pt;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:.25pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:35.4pt;line-height:\r\n115%\"><b>&nbsp;Yetki Kullanımı</b><o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:7.25pt;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:36.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:\r\n115%;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo2;tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\r\nSymbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol\">·<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]-->Basitleştirilmiş usul yalnızca <b>onaylanmış\r\nihracatçı statüsüne sahip firmalar</b> tarafından kullanılabilir. <o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:7.25pt;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:36.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:\r\n115%;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo2;tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\r\nSymbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol\">·<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]-->Bu yetki <b>yalnızca firmanın kendi ihracat\r\nişlemleri</b> için geçerlidir. <o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:7.25pt;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:.25pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:35.4pt;line-height:\r\n115%\"><b>&nbsp;1 No.lu ve 13 No.lu Hanelerin Uyumu</b><o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:7.25pt;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:36.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:\r\n115%;mso-list:l3 level1 lfo3;tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\r\nSymbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol\">·<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]-->A.TR belgesinin: <o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:7.25pt;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:72.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:\r\n115%;mso-list:l3 level2 lfo3;tab-stops:list 72.0pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\r\n&quot;Courier New&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Courier New&quot;\">o<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><b>1\r\nno.lu hanesinde yer alan firma bilgisi</b> ile <o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:7.25pt;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:72.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:\r\n115%;mso-list:l3 level2 lfo3;tab-stops:list 72.0pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\r\n&quot;Courier New&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Courier New&quot;\">o<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><b>13\r\nno.lu hanede yer alan beyan</b><br>\r\nuyumlu olmalıdır. <o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:7.25pt;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:36.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:\r\n115%;mso-list:l3 level1 lfo3;tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\r\nSymbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol\">·<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]-->Uyumsuzluk halinde belge reddedilebilmektedir. <o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:7.25pt;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:.25pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:35.4pt;line-height:\r\n115%\"><b>&nbsp;Dolaylı Temsil Durumu</b><o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:7.25pt;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:36.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:\r\n115%;mso-list:l4 level1 lfo4;tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\r\nSymbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol\">·<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]-->Onaylanmış ihracatçı yetkisi olmayan bir\r\nfirmanın, bu yetkiye sahip başka bir firma aracılığıyla basitleştirilmiş\r\nusulden yararlanması <b>mümkün değildir</b>. <o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:7.25pt;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:36.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:\r\n115%;mso-list:l4 level1 lfo4;tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\r\nSymbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol\">·<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]-->Bu şekilde düzenlenen belgeler ithalatta <b>teknik\r\nnedenle reddedilir</b>. <o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:7.25pt;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:36.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:\r\n115%;mso-list:l4 level1 lfo4;tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\r\nSymbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol\">·<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]-->Ancak dolaylı temsilci: <o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:7.25pt;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:72.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:\r\n115%;mso-list:l4 level2 lfo4;tab-stops:list 72.0pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\r\n&quot;Courier New&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Courier New&quot;\">o<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]-->Normal\r\nusulde düzenlenen A.TR belgelerinde <o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:7.25pt;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:72.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:\r\n115%;mso-list:l4 level2 lfo4;tab-stops:list 72.0pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\r\n&quot;Courier New&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Courier New&quot;\">o<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]-->13\r\nno.lu haneyi ihracatçı adına doldurabilir. <o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:7.25pt;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:.25pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:35.4pt;line-height:\r\n115%\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:7.25pt;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:.25pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:35.4pt;line-height:\r\n115%\"><b>İstisnai Durum (Temsil Yoluyla İmzalama)</b><br>\r\nZorunlu hallerde;<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:7.25pt;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:36.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:\r\n115%;mso-list:l2 level1 lfo5;tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\r\nSymbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol\">·<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]-->Belgenin <b>onaylanmış ihracatçıya ait sevkiyat\r\niçin düzenlenmiş olması</b>, <o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:7.25pt;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:36.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:\r\n115%;mso-list:l2 level1 lfo5;tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\r\nSymbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol\">·<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]-->13 no.lu hanede <b>temsil edildiğinin açıkça\r\nbelirtilmesi</b>, <o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:7.25pt;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:36.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:\r\n115%;mso-list:l2 level1 lfo5;tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\r\nSymbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol\">·<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]-->Asıl ihracatçının (onaylanmış ihracatçı) <b>tam\r\nunvanının yer alması</b>, <o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:7.25pt;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:.25pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:35.4pt;line-height:\r\n115%\">şartıyla, 13 no.lu hanenin temsilci tarafından doldurulması mümkündür.<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:7.25pt;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:.25pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:35.4pt;line-height:\r\n115%\">Bu durumda, belgeden asıl ihracatçının açık şekilde anlaşılabilmesi ve\r\nbaşka bir şüphe bulunmaması halinde belge kabul edilebilir. <o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:7.25pt;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:.25pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:35.4pt;line-height:\r\n115%\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:7.25pt;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:.25pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:35.4pt;line-height:\r\n115%\"><br>\r\nSöz konusu hususlar halihazırda yürürlükte olup uygulamada dikkate alınması\r\ngerekmektedir.<o:p></o:p></p>\n                                <a target=\"_blank\" class=\"text-danger\" href=\"http://portal.ugm.com.tr/shared/dosyaal.ashx?arsivid=1112f981-9b02-4fe7-a1c0-fb1cd3d15771&amp;refno=REF0248.rar\">\n                                    http://portal.ugm.com.tr/shared/dosyaal.ashx?arsivid=1112f981-9b02-4fe7-a1c0-fb1cd3d15771&amp;refno=REF0248.rar\n                                </a>"}
